何人都唔應該響普世價值上助紂為虐、自我審查！）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你響twitter大海中唔知retweet咩好<br />\ntwitter 組整左個bot<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=02aa91a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你入    /task2</span></span><br />\n就可以搵到以上的新聞<br />\n<br />\nRetweet 加 cm ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得每日做！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你入 /task1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就可以見到人權法新聞同議員的tweet<br />\n<br />\n記得多謝埋人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f20a5a6d27acee1294d36c4f9c336ae5e8ac0b","tid":1661694,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:05:27.000Z","msg":"Sir this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18443b78c7e159d19b2fbd443ffaeb13ccf62b45","tid":1661694,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:05:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fac698ad0e6c4017bede0a6509c7927f748a2b1","tid":1661694,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"可能會卡在麥康奈爾手上，佢老婆係支那人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cTvTisEoEpw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcTvTisEoEpw&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLizw1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=27ceff29\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cTvTisEoEpw</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n【FC】西九站遊行係中共真春袋！<span style=\"color: red;\">需要針對強國文宣<strong>輸出革命</strong></span>！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661232\" target=\"_blank\">https://l